= class GLib::TcpConnection

== Object Hierarchy

* Object
  * GLib::Instantiatable
    * GLib::Object
      * GLib::IOStream
        * GLib::SocketConnection
          * GLib::TcpConnection

== Instance Methods

--- graceful_disconnect=(graceful_disconnect)

    Sets the value whether or not close does a graceful disconnect or not.
     * graceful_disconnect: true if or not close does a graceful disconnect
     * Returns: graceful_disconnect

--- graceful_disconnect?

    Gets the value whether or not close does a graceful disconnect or not.
     * Returns: true if or not close does a graceful disconnect

--- set_graceful_disconnect(graceful_disconnect)

    Same as graceful_disconnect=.
     * graceful_disconnect: true if or not close does a graceful disconnect
     * Returns: self

== Properties

--- graceful-disconnect: true or false (Read/Write)

    Whether or not close does a graceful disconnect

